Features
--------

* APRSD Plugin that gets a stock quote from Yahoo Finance python API and returns that.


Installation
------------

You can install *APRSD Yahoo Finance Stock Quotes* via pip_ from PyPI_:

.. code:: console

   $ pip install aprsd-stock-plugin


